snippet.title: [Procelio] "Experimental Warfare" Update 1.3a
snippet.description:
Welcome back friends!

It's been a while but we have created, specially for you, a new update for the game!
Containing a whole bunch of improvements and new things, you can read about it in detail on our website below :)
